org.modelio.metamodel.uml.behavior.stateMachineModel

Interface InternalTransition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<MObject>, Element, MObject, ModelElement, Transition, UmlModelElement

    public interface InternalTransition
extends Transition
    InternalTransition v0.0.9054 This Transition is related to a State. It can be triggered when entering or exiting the State, or can describe an activity that is performed whilst in the State (do Transitions). A Transition belongs to its origin StateVertex.
